---
title: Ribeye and Roasted Garlic Pan Sauce with Mashed Potatoes and Green Beans
description: If you’re serious about steak, you know that ribeye is the crème de la crème. Our chefs took it to the next level by topping it with an equally luxurious pan sauce. Here, roasted garlic and rich beef demi-glace mingle with the fond—the crispy bits and drippings left by the seared steak—to create a condiment that you’ll want to drizzle over just about everything. Speaking of delicious things to drizzle with sauce, we’re serving up sides of chive-flecked mashed potatoes and crisp roasted green beans.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ribeye-and-roasted-garlic-pan-sauce-a08e1a63.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/ribeye-and-roasted-garlic-pan-sauce-5d92103c8a9c39110644b9a7-11911def.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/ribeye-and-roasted-garlic-pan-sauce-5d92103c8a9c39110644b9a7
course: main course
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 1210 kcal
  fat: 88 g
  saturated fat: 39 g
